name: Spooky On The Moon issue 1/2/3
description:
Here, complete, is issue 1, 2 and 3 (Price includes UK postage).

Issue #1 : Part 1 of the interview with Frances Mckee (from The Vaselines), a four page comic and a report on legendary rockers 'The Zombees'.

Issue #2 : Part 2 of the interview with Frances Mckee, a review of The Dead Weather and shocking news on the future of The Zombees.

Issue #3 : A huge review of Electric Warrior by T.Rex, some illustrations and a tour report from The Zombees huge European Monster Tour. 

Also includes A4 poster.

name: Pin Ups
